{"tid":1299611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下雨天 要護鞋","createTime":"2019-07-09T05:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:49:07.000Z","uid":76332,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2245293c0ac20bc57f9ebef42cdc65553d82c7ec","tid":1299611,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"香港嘅夏天潮濕又多雨 唔想整污糟你對靚鞋？咁就要買對膠鞋套喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yJK6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yJK6i.jpg&h=3c18569f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網打 防水 鞋套 就會搵到 幾十蚊就有一對 仲可以循環再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議買黑色</span> 因為最襟污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋黑色吸熱 可以加強腳板底嘅血液循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要買就快喇 呢排陰晴不定 好快就會落下一場大雨喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc4bdedc9de09960bda2173a3368389d03927d0","tid":1299611,"uid":137459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee2ef9a961d24eea7b7da90f090fa614cda4a57a","tid":1299611,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"頂 開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359f41ac7e7ac64f9aefecae057b07161a90fb22","tid":1299611,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"保護靚鞋 人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5c2f5f372cebfc42c2aa92e19964afd35eb74e","tid":1299611,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src